Method behavioural specifications:
- The integer array parameter `strength` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `strength` length is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100000.
- All values in the integer array parameter `strength` are greater than or equal to 1 and are less than or equal to 1000000000.
- The integer result is the sum of the total strengths of all contiguous groups of wizards modulo 1000000007.